Name: lam
Description: Component of base CoTS mortality attributable to age dependence

Name: Ble_imp_f
Description: Option for impulse bleaching mortality for fast-growing corals

Name: Ble_imp_m
Description: Option for impulse bleaching mortality for slow-growing corals

Name: p1m
Description: Mortality of slow-growing corals induced by a CoTS

Name: rm
Description: Slow-growing coral intrinsic growth rate

Name: Cm_init
Description: Initialised massive slow-growing corals

Name: p1f
Description: Mortality of fast-growing corals induced by a CoTS

Name: Cf_init
Description: Initialised branching fast-growing corals

Name: CoTS_init
Description: Starting CoTS numbers

Name: h_stock_recruitment
Description: Slope of stock recruitment curve

Name: ptil
Description: CoTS mortality linked to fast-growing coral availability

Name: rf
Description: Fast-growing coral intrinsic growth rate

Name: sigCoTS
Description: Assumed variability in CoTS recruitment

Name: Imm_CoTS
Description: Background base immigration rate

Name: R0
Description: Recruitment in unexploited population

Name: Eta_m
Description: Slope of bleaching mortality curve for slow-growing corals

Name: Mcots
Description: Instantaneous CoTS mortality

Name: SST_sig_f
Description: Variability of branching fast-growing corals growth about optimum

Name: Eta_f
Description: Slope of bleaching mortality curve for fast-growing corals

Name: AgeClasses
Description: Number of CoTS age classes; index = age

Name: SST_sig_m
Description: Variability of massive slow-growing corals growth about optimum

Name: switchSlope
Description: Shape parameter that control slope of prey switching function

Name: p2m
Description: Slow-growing predation density-dependence decay constant

Name: p2f
Description: Fast-growing predation density-dependence decay constant

Name: SST0_f
Description: Optimal growth SST for branching fast-growing corals

Name: NumYrs
Description: Number of years; index = yr

Name: SST_optim
Description: Optimal sea surface temperature for coral growth rate

Name: SST0_m
Description: Optimal growth SST for massive slow-growing corals

Name: M_SST50_f
Description: SST at which observe 50 % mortality of fast-growing corals

Name: M_SST50_m
Description: SST at which observe 50 % mortality of slow-growing corals

Name: first_yr
Description: first year of simulation

Name: first_yr_dat
Description: first year data

Name: last_yr
Description: last year of simulation

Name: last_yr_dat
Description: last year data

Name: Cots_K
Description: COTS Carrying capacity

Name: age
Description: index of 'AgeClasses' dimension. Age class of Crown of Thorns (COTS)

Name: index
Description: index

Name: yr
Description: index of 'NumYrs' dimension. Which is the current year of the simulation.

Name: N_cots
Description: Age-structured CoTS biomass. AgeClass 1 is recruits. AgeClass 2 is juveniles. AgeClass 3 is sexually mature adults.

Name: Imm_res
Description: Vector for immigration residuals

Name: Rcots
Description: Annual CoTS recruitment

Name: M_CoTS_age
Description: Age-dependent CoTS mortality

Name: f_mortality
Description: Multiplier representing impact of coral abundance on CoTS mortality

Name: alpha
Description: Beverton-Holt shape parameter expressed in terms of slope steepness

Name: M_ble_f
Description: Bleaching mortality term on fast growing corals
Value: (yr+first_yr<=last_yr_dat) ? (std::min(Cf(yr) * (1.0 / (1.0 + exp(-Eta_f * (SST_dat(yr) - M_SST50_f)))), Cf(yr) - 0.001)):(std::min(Cf(yr) * (1.0 / (1.0 + exp(-Eta_f * (SST_optim - M_SST50_f)))), Cf(yr) - 0.001))

Name: rho_SST_F
Description: SST on intrinsic growth rate of fast growing corals

Name: rho_SST_M
Description: SST on intrinsic growth rate of slow growing corals

Name: M_ble_m
Description: Bleaching mortality term on slow growing corals
Value: (yr+first_yr<=last_yr_dat)?(std::min(Cm(yr) * (1.0 / (1.0 + exp(-Eta_m * (SST_dat(yr) - M_SST50_m)))), Cm(yr) - 0.001)):(std::min(Cm(yr) * (1.0 / (1.0 + exp(-Eta_m* (SST_optim - M_SST50_m)))), Cm(yr) - 0.001))

Name: immigration
Description: Immigration pulse in 1994; Recruitment deviations

Name: Imm_res_yrs
Description: Pulses of CoTS recuits (immigration or self-recruitment)

Name: Cf
Description: Fast-growing coral

Name: Qf
Description: CoTS predation on fast growing corals, Cf

Name: Cm
Description: Slow-growing coral

Name: Qm
Description: CoTS predation on slow growing corals, Cm

Name: SPR0
Description: Spawners per recruit in unexploited population

Name: rho
Description: Switch function

Name: beta
Description: Beverton-Holt shape parameter expressed in terms of slope steepness

Name: dummy
Description: dummy variable. DO NOT CHANGE

Name: Kots_sp
Description: Coral feeding CoTS in unexploited population (age-1/age-2+)

Value: Cm(yr) * exp(-Cots_K * Qm(yr) - M_ble_m * rho_SST_M * SST_dat(yr)) + rm * Cf(yr) * (1 - rho * Cm(yr))
